# YouTube Data API v3 key — powers the live view/like counts on the reels.
#
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com  → create a project.
# 2. "APIs & Services" → "Enable APIs" → enable "YouTube Data API v3".
# 3. "Credentials" → "Create credentials" → "API key".
# 4. Restrict the key → "Application restrictions: HTTP referrers" and add:
#       http://localhost:*        (for local dev)
#       https://nixthevixen.github.io/*   (for the live site)
#    Also under "API restrictions" limit it to "YouTube Data API v3".
#
# For LOCAL dev:  copy this file to `.env.local` and paste your key below.
# For the LIVE site: add the key as a GitHub Actions secret named
#   VITE_YT_API_KEY  (repo → Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions).
#
VITE_YT_API_KEY=
